{"tid":1467702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家記住呢九個字","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:29:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:59:52.000Z","uid":232728,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ee897119e31a58e8beb6b2746639c040efaee701","tid":1467702,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:29:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化 不篤灰</span></strong></span><br />\n呢九個字由6月開始已經係呢場運動嘅一個<span style=\"color: red;\">大原則</span>，點解近呢一個禮拜大家好似唔記得晒咁？越嚟越多互相指責嘅po，大家係咪唔記得咗呢九個字喇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每個人都一定有唔同意見，一定會唔同意某啲做法，但係<span style=\"color: red;\">唔需要因為唔同意而去指責人地</span>。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無大台</span>亦都係呢場運動嘅另一大原則。無大台嘅好處係咩？就係可以集思廣益，可以<span style=\"color: red;\">運用晒咁多人嘅智慧</span>去打贏場仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家要好好運用呢一點，去<span style=\"color: red;\">提出自己嘅意見</span>令大家<span style=\"color: red;\">互相檢討</span>時亦令大家<span style=\"color: red;\">進步</span>，而唔係互相指責去<span style=\"color: red;\">打沉自己人</span>呀。<br />\n唔好再互相指責好冇喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地冇互相指責嘅本錢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家要記得團結一致先可以打贏呢場仗呀！引用番其他人嘅說話：由呢刻開始，只有互相檢討，沒有互相指責。亦都冇分和理非勇武定文宣，只有香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人加油</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你睇到呢一到 多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a64e3224dae52a7073757413fb12d1f3e40d29db","tid":1467702,"uid":203619,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:29:56.000Z","msg":"我只推 正常POST<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/RfNfTgW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRfNfTgW.png&h=52691539&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日我留意到最大單係警察係機場用槍指嚇市民<br />\n你地又留意到咩呢?<br />\n希望大家理性啲 幫手推返正常POST<br />\n<br />\n一句講哂<br />\n鬼係捉唔哂，大局為重"},{"pid":"70f8fe1342e4b7348f880333e993172de9a858ad","tid":1467702,"uid":8584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:30:16.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n我地要檢討 善後 唔係互屌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時刻保持冷靜 獨立思考！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔該大家檢討行動唔好用d鬧人既語氣 字眼！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dDEnyS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dDEnyS</a></span>"},{"pid":"977633562f3f4cc00b98a6579dbe7e1c0c9fee9e","tid":1467702,"uid":1915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:30:17.000Z","msg":"共狗最撚叻<span style=\"color: red;\">枱面交戲枱底郁手</span><br />\n復仇都要冷靜<br />\n唔係要鏡頭前直播打爆人眼<br />\n係要敵人<span style=\"color: red;\">雙眼入巷單眼出</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">私了既野唔應該係國際舞台出現</span><br />\n<br />\n出面果班屌自己人同警犬有乜分別既全部都係痴線<br />\n執法系統已經失效既社會仲講唔好變成佢地<br />\n咁公義由邊個去彰顯？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">枱面和你飛 枱底私了</span></span>"},{"pid":"66bdc535dc4b0eb487366ca8646254e6a52a1e60","tid":1467702,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba4fbacda9dcf9450549a6818b00af92232cd0e","tid":1467702,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08